Title: Let's Not Worry Her
Description:
Right, we better get back to Haimaz before she gets suspicious.

Please, don't tell her about any of this. Her duty is to guide and guard me in my role as compiler. 

If she knew I was planning to leave... I don't know what she would do.
ObjectivesText: Return to Haimaz in Shadowvein Point.
RewardText: Thank you for bringing him back. He always acts strange when we come to Shadowvein Point, but he seems more out of sorts than usual.
